oked around himself. He wondered if anyone on this planet were fighting, an=
d then he thought about how nice it would be if there was no more fighting.=
 He had done his fair share of it, and would much like to retire, yet live =
peacefully in a peaceful universe, but to do that he had to end the war bet=
ween Maximal and Predacon. He looked around the landscape for any nearby fr=
iends or foes...

Pinsir was aboard Scyther's ship, and was waiting to join=
...the...Predacons... (Hint hint, Zardus!)
